        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Smarter Pretrial Detention for Drug Charges Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill removes the presumption of pretrial detention for an individual who is charged with a federal drug offense for which the maximum term of imprisonment is 10 years or more.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
